        <h4 style="text-align: center;">Ticketing System</h4>
         <p class="para-1">A ticketing system is a software platform designed to manage and track customer support requests. It streamlines the process of resolving customer issues, making it easier for businesses to provide fast and effective support. With a ticketing system, customers can submit support requests through multiple channels, including email, phone, or a web portal. The requests are then organized and prioritized, allowing support teams to respond quickly and efficiently.</p>
